<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   GM Recalls 911,000 Cars for Defects,
   Even as Ads Tout Its Autos' Quality
   ----
   By Jacqueline Mitchell and Neal Templin
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/04/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
<CO>
   GM
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
<IN>
AUTO PARTS AND EQUIPMENT INCLUDING TIRES (AUP)
